Package de.hsa.jam.ui

Class Summary
AbstractView This class provides the base level abstraction for views in this example.
ChromaticTunerFrame Class implements a JFrame with a basic chromatic tuner.
CustomFileFilter A convenience implementation of FileFilter that filters out all files except for those type extensions that it knows about.
MainWindow This class implements the MainFrame of the application.
There is a menu, a userpanel with rec/play, the scorepanel and a prefenence frame
MetronomeFrame This class implements a JFrame with a basic metronome.
ScorePanel This class implements a ScorePanel.
Based on abcnotation and abc4j it draws the detected notes.
SimplePlotterFrame Simple JFrame to plot float arrays in a thread
